# File: app/styles/desktop.css.ab
# Purpose: Minified single-line compiled application stylesheet for desktop views — legacy app/styles/ location
# Dependencies: []

## Overview
A single-line minified version of the compiled desktop stylesheet. This is the compressed form of what is expanded in `app/assets/css/desktop.css`. Located in the older `app/styles/` Compass output directory. Contains the full desktop layout CSS including the CSS reset, ProximaNova fonts, navbar, grid overrides, and all desktop-specific view styles.

## Interface
No exports. Stylesheet file — loaded as a `<link>` tag.

## Dependencies
No project-level `.ab` dependencies. Requires ProximaNova font files at `../fonts/proximanova-*.ttf`.

## Implementation Notes
- Single-line minified (1 line) — the expanded form is `app/assets/css/desktop.css` (8468 lines)
- Located in the older `app/styles/` Compass output directory
- The expanded `app/assets/css/desktop.css` is the authoritative source
- Compiled from `app/assets/scss/` SCSS source files via Compass
